[4] Indiana (Hamilton County)
Date: Tue 4 Oct 2022
Source: Practical Horseman [abridged, edited]
https://practicalhorsemanmag.com/health-archive/ph-edcc-health-watch/strangles-at-indiana-horse-boarding-facility/


On 3 Oct 2022, an attending veterinarian confirmed a horse positive for strangles at a boarding facility in Hamilton County, Indiana. Five horses are suspected positive, and 17 horses were exposed. The facility is under voluntary quarantine.

--
